Package de.jvstvshd.localstream.title

Class TitleMetadata

java.lang.Object
de.jvstvshd.localstream.title.TitleMetadata
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public class TitleMetadata extends Object implements Cloneable
Contains metadata for titles (the rate, the name of the file/de.jvstvshd.localstream.scheduling.title, the length in seconds, the size in bytes and the internal id). Important note: This class contains several deprecated features that are marked with forRemoval = true. These features will be removed and should not be used.
See Also:
TitleMetadata.Builder, builder()
